20
00:01:51,786 --> 00:01:57,375
<i>- Aku tetap akan menunggumu
- Aku tetap akan menunggumu</i>

21
00:01:57,458 --> 00:02:01,921
<i>- Aku tetap senyum walau terseksa
- Aku tetap senyum walau terseksa</i>

22
00:02:02,005 --> 00:02:07,760
<i>- Hatiku bertahan demimu
- Hatiku bertahan demimu</i>

23
00:02:08,261 --> 00:02:10,346
<i>- Aku menangis setiap hari
- Aku menangis setiap hari</i>

24
00:02:10,430 --> 00:02:12,682
<i>- Tapi gembira bertemumu
- Tapi gembira bertemumu</i>

25
00:02:13,391 --> 00:02:18,604
<i>Kau sangat indah sempurna</i>

26
00:02:18,688 --> 00:02:23,192
<i>Aku berbangga jadi milikmu seorang</i>

27
00:02:23,276 --> 00:02:24,277
Shin Sol-i!

28
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:26,821
<i>- Aku dulunya muram
- Aku dulunya muram</i>

29
00:02:26,904 --> 00:02:29,240
<i>- Kini tersenyum selalu
- Kini tersenyum selalu</i>

30
00:02:29,324 --> 00:02:33,453
<i>- Apa yang kau dah lakukan kepadaku?
- Apa yang kau dah lakukan kepadaku?</i>

31
00:02:33,536 --> 00:02:36,372
<i>- Janji kepadaku
- Janji kepadaku</i>

32
00:02:36,456 --> 00:02:39,375
<i>- Hingga penghujung dunia ini
- Hingga penghujung dunia ini</i>

33
00:02:39,876 --> 00:02:46,883
<i>- Sayangiku diriku seorang saja
- Sayangiku diriku seorang saja</i>

34
00:02:48,217 --> 00:02:49,594
Berapa? Dapat 100 markah?

35
00:02:49,677 --> 00:02:50,595
Betulkah 100?

36
00:02:51,304 --> 00:02:52,847
- Ya!
- Kita berjaya!

37
00:02:57,310 --> 00:02:58,186
BAKI MASA

38
00:02:58,269 --> 00:02:59,896
Tinggal seminit.

39
00:03:09,947 --> 00:03:10,948
KARAOKE SSONG

40
00:03:11,032 --> 00:03:13,451
- Helo?
<i>- Kamu di mana</i>?

41
00:03:13,534 --> 00:03:14,952
<i>Pertandingan semakin hampir.</i>

42
00:03:16,162 --> 00:03:17,705
Jangan risau. Saya balik sekarang.

43
00:03:21,125 --> 00:03:23,669
Kenapa? Ada sesuatu berlaku?

44
00:03:24,545 --> 00:03:25,505
Tak ada apa.

45
00:03:25,588 --> 00:03:28,216
Kawan, ini kali pertama saya berkaraoke.

46
00:03:28,299 --> 00:03:29,926
Betulkah?

47
00:03:30,009 --> 00:03:32,845
Ketika di kem latihan
kami tak dibenarkan keluar.

48
00:03:32,929 --> 00:03:35,890
Habislah. Lepas ini
tentu kamu semua nak pergi lagi.

49
00:03:38,392 --> 00:03:40,937
Hujung minggu ini
ada pertandingan renang. Nak datang?

50
00:03:41,020 --> 00:03:42,188
Apa?

51
00:03:45,108 --> 00:03:46,484
Berapa harganya?

52
00:03:47,235 --> 00:03:48,820
Tentulah percuma.

53
00:03:48,903 --> 00:03:50,571
Datanglah. Saya belanja makan.

54
00:03:50,655 --> 00:03:53,116
Ini tak adil. Awak belanja Sol-i saja?

55
00:03:53,199 --> 00:03:55,368
Tentulah kamu semua juga.

56
00:03:55,451 --> 00:03:56,536
Datanglah.

57
00:03:56,619 --> 00:03:59,163
Okey. Kami akan pergi dan beri sokongan.

58
00:03:59,914 --> 00:04:03,793
Tapi kenapa saya rasa seram sejuk?

59
00:04:03,876 --> 00:04:05,503
Kenapa? Maksud awak?

60
00:04:06,212 --> 00:04:07,463
Cikgu.

61
00:04:18,349 --> 00:04:20,518
Apa nombor laluan saya?

62
00:04:21,144 --> 00:04:23,729
Aduhai, kenapa? Kenapa saya tak ingat?

63
00:04:23,813 --> 00:04:25,523
Basikal saya dah hilang.

64
00:04:30,236 --> 00:04:31,529
Hati-hati!

65
00:04:32,029 --> 00:04:34,157
Tinggalkan saja!

66
00:04:36,409 --> 00:04:37,535
Aduhai.

67
00:04:38,536 --> 00:04:39,412
Naiklah.

68
00:04:58,723 --> 00:05:00,308
Basikal kamu hilang?

69
00:05:00,808 --> 00:05:03,478
Basikal itu masih agak baru,
tapi hilang lagi?

70
00:05:04,103 --> 00:05:05,188
Mari sini.

71
00:05:05,271 --> 00:05:07,482
Mak, sabar. Itu juga bahaya!

72
00:05:07,565 --> 00:05:10,109
Silap langkah, ia boleh membunuh!

73
00:05:10,193 --> 00:05:12,778
Baguslah, kamu memang patut diajar.
Mari sini!

74
00:05:12,862 --> 00:05:13,863
Saya bersalah.

75
00:05:13,946 --> 00:05:15,406
Ayah, tolong saya.

76
00:05:15,490 --> 00:05:18,159
Macam mana basikal itu boleh hilang?

77
00:05:18,242 --> 00:05:20,870
Saya ke kedai buku
untuk beli buku latihan.

78
00:05:20,953 --> 00:05:23,915
Tapi ada banyak kes kecurian di situ.

79
00:05:23,998 --> 00:05:27,793
Dia ke kedai buku untuk beli buku.
Itu untuk pelajaran dia juga.

80
00:05:27,877 --> 00:05:30,463
Tengoklah kamu anak-beranak berpakat.

81
00:05:30,546 --> 00:05:32,840
Apa gunanya bersengkang mata cipta resipi?

82
00:05:32,924 --> 00:05:34,800
Kamu berdua sibuk habiskan duit.

83
00:05:34,884 --> 00:05:37,053
Janganlah cakap begitu.

84
00:05:37,136 --> 00:05:38,888
Saya banyak bantu awak.

85
00:05:38,971 --> 00:05:41,390
Beli basikal baru hujung minggu ini.

86
00:05:41,474 --> 00:05:43,893
Jangan merengek penat menaiki bas.

87
00:05:45,686 --> 00:05:46,687
Tak perlu!

88
00:05:50,358 --> 00:05:52,652
Saya patut beli basikal baru.

89
00:05:53,486 --> 00:05:56,739
Saya nak naik basikal bersama Heon.
Tapi apa ini?

90
00:05:56,822 --> 00:05:59,408
Sakitnya kaki.

91
00:06:00,368 --> 00:06:01,827
- Kawan!
- Hei.

92
00:06:02,828 --> 00:06:04,121
Hai.

93
00:06:04,622 --> 00:06:07,875
Tentu susah sebab awak tak ada basikal.

94
00:06:08,709 --> 00:06:11,629
Taklah. Saya sedang renung kesilapan saya.

95
00:06:11,712 --> 00:06:13,506
Nak saya jemput setiap pagi?

96
00:06:14,298 --> 00:06:15,466
Tak apalah.

97
00:06:17,385 --> 00:06:18,511
Kalau awak sedih,

98
00:06:18,594 --> 00:06:21,931
apa perkara yang boleh ceriakan awak?

99
00:06:22,014 --> 00:06:23,474
Entahlah.

100
00:06:24,934 --> 00:06:26,060
Ketika sedih,

101
00:06:26,602 --> 00:06:29,188
bukankah dah memadai jika kita ada teman?

102
00:06:29,272 --> 00:06:31,232
Yakah?

103
00:06:31,315 --> 00:06:32,358
Ya.

104
00:06:40,950 --> 00:06:42,785
BIAR SAYA TOLONG!

105
00:06:47,623 --> 00:06:49,750
Syabas, semua.

106
00:06:49,834 --> 00:06:54,088
Cikgu amat tersentuh dengan
karangan kamu semua.

107
00:06:54,839 --> 00:06:57,466
Terutamanya Hui-ji dan Cha Heon.

108
00:06:57,550 --> 00:07:01,387
Karangan mereka berdua hebat

109
00:07:01,470 --> 00:07:03,264
seperti penulis profesional.

110
00:07:03,347 --> 00:07:07,685
Jadi apa kata kita minta Sol-i
untuk bacakan karangan ini?

111
00:07:09,603 --> 00:07:11,647
- Saya?
- Tolong bacakan.

112
00:07:14,233 --> 00:07:15,234
Baiklah.

113
00:07:18,112 --> 00:07:19,405
NAMA: CHA HEON

114
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:26,537
"Sewaktu berusia lapan tahun,

115
00:07:26,621 --> 00:07:29,373
saya pernah tersesat.

116
00:07:30,082 --> 00:07:32,918
Ikutkan hati
terasa seperti ingin menangis,

117
00:07:33,002 --> 00:07:35,755
tapi saya beritahu diri
saya takkan sesekali menangis.

118
00:07:36,756 --> 00:07:38,341
Setelah masa berlalu,

119
00:07:39,258 --> 00:07:41,177
<i>- ayah datang mendapatkan saya."</i>
- Heon!

120
00:07:41,260 --> 00:07:42,511
Ayah!

121
00:07:42,595 --> 00:07:45,389
<i>"Air mata yang dipendam
akhirnya berguguran.</i>

122
00:07:45,890 --> 00:07:47,975
<i>- Melihat anaknya menangis,"</i>
- Jangan takut.

123
00:07:48,059 --> 00:07:50,269
<i>- "ayah mendakap saya dengan mesra."</i>
- Ayah ada.

124
00:07:51,437 --> 00:07:54,148
<i>"Ayah bawa saya ke sebuah restoran Cina</i>

125
00:07:54,231 --> 00:07:57,318
<i>dan bersama kami nikmati
</i>jajangmyeon<i> kegemaran saya.</i>

126
00:07:58,319 --> 00:08:00,112
<i>Sambil berjalan pulang,</i>

127
00:08:00,196 --> 00:08:04,158
<i>genggaman tangan ayah
terasa begitu hangat.</i>

128
00:08:11,290 --> 00:08:15,044
Itulah saat paling panjang
pernah saya habiskan berdua

129
00:08:15,795 --> 00:08:20,091
bersama ayah saya
yang sentiasa di luar mencari rezeki."

130
00:08:26,889 --> 00:08:28,557
Awak masih keluar makan dengan dia?

131
00:08:36,774 --> 00:08:41,028
Heon, kami akan masak <i>bulgogi</i> esok.
Awak nak makan sama?

132
00:08:42,655 --> 00:08:43,739
Tak apalah.

133
00:08:44,657 --> 00:08:46,992
Apa kata kita naik basikal bersama?

134
00:08:47,660 --> 00:08:50,079
Saya takkan ganggu awak.

135
00:08:50,162 --> 00:08:52,415
Lagipun, saya sangat ringan.

136
00:08:52,498 --> 00:08:53,499
Macam mana?

137
00:08:56,001 --> 00:08:57,378
Bawalah basikal ini balik.

138
00:08:58,671 --> 00:08:59,714
Awak nak ke mana?

139
00:09:01,424 --> 00:09:03,134
Saya tak boleh ikut?

140
00:09:04,885 --> 00:09:05,928
Jangan ikut.

141
00:09:46,343 --> 00:09:47,428
Yang ini.

142
00:09:48,304 --> 00:09:50,723
Tentu sukar untuk dia
buat persiapan sendiri.

143
00:09:50,806 --> 00:09:55,895
Ini juga peluang yang baik
untuk ambil hati ibu dia.

144
00:09:57,730 --> 00:10:01,275
Bagaimana perasaan menyukai seseorang?

145
00:10:01,358 --> 00:10:04,779
Saya pun tak pasti.

146
00:10:04,862 --> 00:10:07,698
Apabila dia muncul,
sekeliling saya bertukar gelap

147
00:10:07,782 --> 00:10:10,159
dan dia seorang saja yang berkilauan.

148
00:10:10,242 --> 00:10:13,537
Seperti cahaya yang terpancar
daripada penyanyi idola?

149
00:10:13,621 --> 00:10:14,789
Betul.

150
00:10:35,226 --> 00:10:36,894
Saya tak pesan ini.

151
00:10:42,566 --> 00:10:43,484
Heon!

152
00:10:45,361 --> 00:10:46,862
Saya yang pesan.

153
00:10:55,538 --> 00:10:57,248
KEJOHANAN RENANG KEBANGSAAN
PIALA PRESIDEN KE-25

154
00:10:57,331 --> 00:11:01,335
<i>Selamat datang ke acara yang dinantikan,
pusingan akhir peringkat sekolah tinggi</i>

155
00:11:01,418 --> 00:11:04,421
<i>Kejohanan Renang Kebangsaan
Piala Presiden ke-25.</i>

156
00:11:04,505 --> 00:11:08,008
<i>Tiga hari selepas persaingan sengit,
enam peserta termasuk</i>

157
00:11:08,092 --> 00:11:11,804
<i>bintang baru, Woo Dae-sung
dan Park Min-woo akan bersaing</i>

158
00:11:11,887 --> 00:11:13,973
<i>- pada pusingan akhir yang bakal bermula.</i>
- Gementarnya.

159
00:11:14,056 --> 00:11:15,140
Samalah.

160
00:11:15,891 --> 00:11:19,186
<i>Berjalan masuk ialah
calon utama kejohanan, Woo Dae-sung.</i>

161
00:11:19,270 --> 00:11:23,649
<i>Pemenang pingat emas acara 100 meter
gaya bebas peringkat sekolah menengah.</i>

162
00:11:23,732 --> 00:11:25,276
<i>Lagak penuh mengancam.</i>

163
00:11:25,359 --> 00:11:26,485
- Woo Dae-sung!
<i>- Dia dijangka…</i>

164
00:11:26,569 --> 00:11:28,737
- Woo Dae-sung, semoga berjaya!
<i>- …untuk mengunggulinya.</i>

165
00:11:28,821 --> 00:11:30,030
<i>Kita nantikan!</i>

166
00:11:30,114 --> 00:11:31,282
Woo Dae-sung!

167
00:11:35,953 --> 00:11:38,247
Woo Dae-sung putih melepak!

168
00:11:38,330 --> 00:11:40,874
Woo Dae-sung, juara!

169
00:11:40,958 --> 00:11:42,626
Putih melepak?

170
00:11:42,710 --> 00:11:46,005
Kulitnya bukan putih melepak, tapi lebih…

171
00:11:46,088 --> 00:11:47,131
WOO DAE-SANG PUTIH MELEPAK

172
00:11:47,214 --> 00:11:49,925
- Hati-hati, jangan cedera!
- Apa-apa pingat pun boleh!

173
00:11:50,467 --> 00:11:51,719
<i>Dalam posisi.</i>

174
00:11:53,637 --> 00:11:54,722
<i>Sedia.</i>

175
00:12:00,769 --> 00:12:03,439
Woo Dae-sung!

176
00:12:11,488 --> 00:12:12,531
Tak putih melepak.

177
00:12:12,615 --> 00:12:15,242
- Woo Dae-sung!
- Woo Dae-sung!

178
00:12:29,381 --> 00:12:31,133
Sikit lagi!

179
00:12:44,271 --> 00:12:46,523
1. PARK MIN-WOO
2. WOO DAE-SUNG

180
00:12:51,612 --> 00:12:52,905
<i>Atlet Woo,</i>

181
00:12:52,988 --> 00:12:55,032
awak sentiasa meraih pingat emas.

182
00:12:55,115 --> 00:12:58,786
Apa perasaan awak
setelah memenangi pingat perak?

183
00:13:01,914 --> 00:13:04,583
- Saya minta maaf.
- Woo Dae-sung, awak hebat!

184
00:13:05,376 --> 00:13:07,252
Awak yang terhebat!

185
00:13:07,336 --> 00:13:08,754
Awak hebat!

186
00:13:13,384 --> 00:13:14,343
Awak hebat!

187
00:13:20,265 --> 00:13:22,893
Tempat kedua juga pencapaian yang hebat.

188
00:13:48,961 --> 00:13:51,797
Awak ingin mewakili negara,
tapi tak jaga badan?

189
00:13:52,798 --> 00:13:54,967
Tempat kedua juga pencapaian hebat?

190
00:14:09,064 --> 00:14:10,399
<i>Heon.</i>

191
00:14:10,482 --> 00:14:14,653
<i>Adik kamu sakit.
Nampaknya mak tak dapat pulang ke Korea.</i>

192
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:17,322
<i>Boleh buat upacara memperingati sendirian?</i>

193
00:14:18,157 --> 00:14:20,826
<i>Mak janji akan pulang bulan depan.</i>

194
00:14:28,792 --> 00:14:29,918
Kawan!

195
00:14:30,002 --> 00:14:31,754
Dae-sung, syabas!

196
00:14:31,837 --> 00:14:33,630
Mereka berdua pulang dulu

197
00:14:33,714 --> 00:14:36,508
kerana ada kelas tuisyen
dan aktiviti keluarga.

198
00:14:36,592 --> 00:14:39,011
Tak apa. Awak seorang saja dah mencukupi.

199
00:14:39,094 --> 00:14:40,554
Terima kasih kerana datang.

200
00:14:40,637 --> 00:14:43,015
Awak tak perlu ucap terima kasih.

201
00:14:43,098 --> 00:14:45,309
Betul! Jom saya belanja awak makan.

202
00:14:45,392 --> 00:14:47,227
Okey? Kita makan daging!

203
00:14:47,811 --> 00:14:50,647
Maaflah. Tawaran awak itu menarik,

204
00:14:50,731 --> 00:14:52,816
tapi saya ada hal penting.

205
00:14:52,900 --> 00:14:53,734
Sekejap.

206
00:14:54,943 --> 00:14:56,612
SEMUA OKEY? SAYA AKAN KE SANA SEGERA

207
00:14:58,197 --> 00:14:59,990
Saya perlu pergi sekarang.

208
00:15:00,074 --> 00:15:03,118
Tak apa. Kita boleh makan lain kali.

209
00:15:03,202 --> 00:15:05,037
Saya akan jadi juara dan jom makan sama.

210
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:07,623
Maaf, tapi saya memang ada hal penting.

211
00:15:08,207 --> 00:15:10,667
Lagi satu, tempat kedua juga sangat hebat.

212
00:15:10,751 --> 00:15:13,003
Kenapa orang cuma raikan
tempat pertama saja?

213
00:15:13,087 --> 00:15:14,505
Terima kasih, kawan.

214
00:15:15,339 --> 00:15:17,591
Sebelum awak pergi, tinggalkan itu.

215
00:15:18,425 --> 00:15:19,551
Ini?

216
00:15:19,635 --> 00:15:21,595
Saya tersalah eja. Saya tulis "Dae-sang".

217
00:15:21,678 --> 00:15:23,138
Saya akan buat yang baru.

218
00:15:23,222 --> 00:15:24,389
Saya lebih suka yang ini.

219
00:15:25,099 --> 00:15:27,601
Kalau awak berikan,
saya akan beri pingat ini.

220
00:15:27,684 --> 00:15:31,230
Jangan merepek. Pingat ini sangat penting.

221
00:15:37,611 --> 00:15:40,280
Kita tukar apabila saya
menang pingat emas nanti.

222
00:15:40,364 --> 00:15:41,490
Okey?

223
00:15:44,701 --> 00:15:46,745
<i>Saya okey. Jangan risau.</i>

224
00:15:49,706 --> 00:15:52,835
- Okey. Saya pergi dulu.
- Okey.

225
00:15:52,918 --> 00:15:53,877
Maaf. Jumpa nanti.

226
00:16:00,467 --> 00:16:02,177
WOO DAE-SANG PUTIH MELEPAK

227
00:16:32,207 --> 00:16:33,041
Heon!

228
00:16:34,835 --> 00:16:36,170
Awak belum mula, bukan?

229
00:16:36,253 --> 00:16:37,504
Apa awak buat di sini?

230
00:16:38,422 --> 00:16:39,506
Apa?

231
00:16:41,341 --> 00:16:42,801
Awak dah buat semuanya?

232
00:16:43,427 --> 00:16:45,179
Saya ada beli buah.

233
00:16:45,262 --> 00:16:46,305
Tak apa. Baliklah.

234
00:16:46,388 --> 00:16:50,767
Saya tak sangka awak
akan buat persiapan begitu awal.

235
00:16:50,851 --> 00:16:53,478
Lagipun, mak awak dan Geon
akan sampai selepas jam 7:00.

236
00:16:54,938 --> 00:16:56,940
Saya okey. Tolong pergi.

237
00:17:00,277 --> 00:17:02,029
Awak memang melampau.

238
00:17:02,571 --> 00:17:04,198
Susah sangatkah untuk awak

239
00:17:04,281 --> 00:17:05,574
- minta bantuan?
- Tak perlu.

240
00:17:25,677 --> 00:17:28,513
Walaupun Geon sakit,
tapi Heon juga masih budak.

241
00:17:28,597 --> 00:17:29,932
Bersendirian pada hari begini.

242
00:17:30,015 --> 00:17:32,935
Saya tahulah dia sibuk mencari rezeki,

243
00:17:33,018 --> 00:17:34,937
tapi dah terlalu lama Heon bersendirian.

244
00:17:35,020 --> 00:17:37,272
Tentu ada sebab yang tak dapat dielakkan.

245
00:17:37,356 --> 00:17:39,858
Saya cuma risau saja.

246
00:17:39,942 --> 00:17:40,984
Oh, ya.

247
00:17:42,527 --> 00:17:45,447
Sol-i, ini untuk Heon.
Pergi hantar ke rumahnya.

248
00:17:45,530 --> 00:17:50,452
Betul. Beritahu dia Pn. Lee Chan-hui
yang bijaksana beli khas untuk dia.

249
00:17:50,535 --> 00:17:52,955
Okey, baiklah.

250
00:17:58,627 --> 00:17:59,753
Hei…

251
00:18:00,254 --> 00:18:02,923
Heon…

252
00:18:03,799 --> 00:18:06,718
Awak sengaja biar pintu terbuka
sempena upacara ini?

253
00:18:07,928 --> 00:18:08,929
Saya…

254
00:18:09,513 --> 00:18:14,059
Saya datang sebab mak
suruh saya hantar vitamin untuk awak.

255
00:18:15,686 --> 00:18:19,523
Saya pun nak minta maaf tentang tadi.

256
00:18:20,315 --> 00:18:23,777
Saya tak tahu langsung
mak awak tak dapat pulang…

257
00:20:28,735 --> 00:20:32,364
AKAN BERSAMBUNG

258
00:20:32,447 --> 00:20:35,867
<i>Meninggalkanmu sendiri</i>

259
00:20:35,951 --> 00:20:39,788
<i>Di setiap penjuru gunung</i>

260
00:20:39,871 --> 00:20:46,461
<i>Masa mengajarku agar melepaskanmu pergi</i>

261
00:20:47,671 --> 00:20:52,843
<i>Aku mengingati suara</i>

262
00:20:52,926 --> 00:20:56,138
<i>Seakan suaramu di dalam jiwa</i>

263
00:20:56,221 --> 00:21:02,811
<i>Tapi kenapa aku tak boleh
mengajakmu bersamaku?</i>

264
00:21:02,894 --> 00:21:05,313
<i>Meninggalkanmu…</i>

265
00:21:08,150 --> 00:21:09,151
<i>Ya!</i>

266
00:21:12,154 --> 00:21:13,780
Maaf.

267
00:21:13,864 --> 00:21:15,907
Saya nak tekan butang "Tepukan".

268
00:21:32,340 --> 00:21:34,050
Dah tamat. Jom.

269
00:21:53,612 --> 00:21:55,030
Heon, tolong saya.

270
00:21:55,113 --> 00:21:56,448
Kenapa pula?

271
00:21:56,531 --> 00:21:57,532
Cha Heon!

272
00:21:58,450 --> 00:22:00,285
Awak tendang Cha Heon? Kuat tak?

273
00:22:00,368 --> 00:22:02,412
Kenapa awak murung saja hari ini?

274
00:22:02,496 --> 00:22:04,289
<i>Ke mana perginya semangat awak?</i>

275
00:22:04,372 --> 00:22:06,708
<i>- Nah.
- Terima sajalah.</i>

276
00:22:06,791 --> 00:22:08,251
<i>Hui-ji buat sendiri.</i>

277
00:22:08,335 --> 00:22:09,377
<i>Mana perginya?</i>

278
00:22:10,253 --> 00:22:12,088
<i>- Gila saya dibuatnya.
- Cuba ingat.</i>

279
00:22:12,172 --> 00:22:16,009
<i>Terutamanya Oh Hui-ji dan Lee Su-jin.</i>

280
00:22:16,092 --> 00:22:17,427
Awak buat apa?

281
00:22:18,553 --> 00:22:23,558
Terjemahan sari kata oleh Hazizah Ali

